# This project uses per-app env files. `pnpm setup` copies the examples below
# into place automatically; you normally don't need to touch them.
#
#   apps/api/.env   (from apps/api/.env.example)  — PORT, WEB_ORIGIN, DATABASE_URL, JWT_SECRET, JWT_EXPIRES_IN
#   apps/web/.env   (from apps/web/.env.example)  — VITE_API_URL
#
# For the Docker workflow, the relevant values are set in docker-compose.yml.
